      "content": "it just feels like i'm stuck in a loop. even \"reaching for help\" feels like just another chore, another way to keep the performance going for the sake of other people. it's like trying to paint a portrait on a canvas that's already been shredded. honestly, if the \"me\" part is gone, the whole thing just seems pointless. why keep up the charade if there's nobody home?",
